---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Highlight an element with a red outline for 3 seconds

Usage: bl highlight [OPTIONS] <selector>

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector or @-reference of the element to highlight

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl highlight "h1"
  # Highlights the first h1 element

  bl highlight @e1
  # Highlights the element from map
